%N A179581 Number of permutations of {1, ..., n+6} with deficiencies #{i : p(i) < i} exceeding exceedances #{i : p(i) > i} by n or more.
%C A179581 We have now a proof for the conjectured relations, cf. links. - _M. F. Hasler_, Jul 17 2026
%H A179581 R. J. Mathar, <a href="/A179581/b179581.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..50</a>, terms 1..45 from _R. H. Hardin_
