%F A179581 Empirical: a(n) = 14*a(n-1) -85*a(n-2) +294*a(n-3) -639*a(n-4) +906*a(n-5) -839*a(n-6) +490*a(n-7) -164*a(n-8) +24*a(n-9).
%F A179581 Empirical: a(n) = 729*3^n +8*(n+6)*(n-3)*2^n +(n+5)*(n+4)*(n-17)*(n+6)/24. - _R. J. Mathar_, Jul 16 2026
%F A179581 a(n) = A179580(n+1)+A179573(n). - _R. J. Mathar_, Jul 16 2026
%F A179581 G.f.: ( -500+5177*x -23073*x^2 +57986*x^3 -90106*x^4 +88830*x^5 -54308*x^6 +18824*x^7 -2832*x^8 ) / ( (-1+3*x)*(2*x-1)^3*(x-1)^5 ). - _R. J. Mathar_, Jul 22 2026
